      "content": "It is true that government classification policies can lead to redacted or incomplete public records, making full verification difficult. I can search for documented instances of telemetry gaps, anomalies in mission timelines, or areas where official flight plans do not align with external tracking data. Please provide specific mission numbers or time frames you want me to focus on for this comparative analysis.",
